	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Priorities for a shammy are hit points/ac/resists/wis.<br>Charisma is the biggest waste of your platinum ever.<br>Has no effect on any of the spells we cast except charm animal, and when are you going to use that spell?<br>It doesn't even figure in to whether or not the mob resists the charm, rather how much aggro you receive when the mob breaks charm.<br>It's fairly easy at the higher levels to have your wis over 200 anyhow AND have decent AC/HPS/Resists.<br>But I will tell you the truth, with the aggro we get casting slow you better worry more about hps than wis because for us regen/chloro/growth/replen IS clarity, in a sense, and every hit from a mob is sucking out of your mana pool.<br>And when/if you get can5 you will be doing 1900 damage to yourself for 1200 mana.<br>60 comes around a lot sooner than you think, especially with PoP.<br>/q<br><br>Mephista<br>59 Shaman<br>Povar<br>&nbsp;<br>Mephista D`Monica<br>&lt;Seraphims Vengeance&gt;<br>Povar<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=617033" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=617033</a></td></tr>
